{
  "project_name": "NUC",
  "description": "Project Objective:\nThe Nauru Utilities Corporation (NUC) seeks to develop a mobile application for both Android and iOS platforms to enhance customer engagement and improve service delivery for their utility services. The application will provide users with the ability to top-up prepaid electricity and water meters, view consumption history, receive outage notifications, and make secure payments. Additionally, the app will offer AI-driven insights such as usage predictions and abnormal consumption detection.\nPlatform:\nMobile App (Android and iOS)\nUser Types and Brief Description:\nCustomers (Residential/Commercial/Industrial/Government):\nPurpose: Users can register, top-up prepaid electricity and water meters, view consumption history, and receive real-time notifications about outages and billing alerts. The app also allows users to track their usage, manage multiple accounts, and perform secure transactions.\nAdmin\nPurpose: Admins will have access to a web-based dashboard to manage user accounts, monitor transactions, send push notifications, and generate reports related to app usage, top-ups, and outages.\nTechnical Functional Features of Each User: \nCustomer Features:\nUser Registration & Login:\nMulti-factor authentication (MFA), email/mobile number verification.\nPassword reset and recovery options.\nOne-click sign-up using mobile number or email.\nAccount Linking:\nLink electricity meters and water tank accounts using meter/account numbers.\nSupport for multiple accounts under a single user profile (e.g., multiple meters or tanks).\n",
